    "description": "Blast your way through waves of alien ships in this retro-inspired space shoot'em up.  Blast It-All features the classic look of old school arcade games, with an updated scoring system that will keep you coming back for more.  Perfect each wave, defeat multiple unique bosses and get the high score. Can you Blast It-All!\n\nFEATURES:\n- 100 waves of enemies\n- Power ups\n- 5 Bosses\n- Online Leaderboards\n- Easy and Normal Modes\n- Unlockable Bossrush Mode\n\n\nJun 2017 Update (v1.7):\n\nChanges, Additions & Fixes:\n- Rework of the second boss (new graphics and effects).\n- Updated all game background graphics, creating a more consistent retro look. \n- Added an effect when player shots hit an enemy. \n- Added a \"Play Again\" button to the game over screen, to provide an easy way to restart the game in the current mode.\n- Minor adjustment to the second boss's movement speed (lowered).",
